OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782373690
OL,3,CParents of baby who died at nursery
OL,4,Cwelcome 3,000 extra surprise Ofsted
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FThe parents of a nine-month-old who
OL,8,Fdied at a nursery have welcomed the
OL,9,Fnews an extra 3,000 surprise Ofsted
OL,10,Fvisits will happen each year in an
OL,11,Feffort to spot risks early.
OL,13,FGenevieve Meehan, known as Gigi, died
OL,14,Fat nine-months-old after being tightly
OL,15,Fswaddled and strapped face down on a
OL,16,Fbeanbag for more than an hour and a
OL,17,Fhalf at a nursery in Cheadle Hulme, in
OL,18,FStockport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782373690
OL,3,CParents of baby who died at nursery
OL,4,Cwelcome 3,000 extra surprise Ofsted
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FSince her death her parents - Katie
OL,8,Fand John - have begun a campaign for
OL,9,Fsafer early years settings, which
OL,10,Fincludes mandatory CCTV, more frequent
OL,11,Finspections for nurseries, and clear,
OL,12,Fstatutory safe sleep guidance.
OL,14,FIn a statement on social media, the
OL,15,FCampaign for Gigi, said it was another
OL,16,Fmajor milestone in their mission to
OL,17,Fkeep young children safe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782373690
OL,3,CParents of baby who died at nursery
OL,4,Cwelcome 3,000 extra surprise Ofsted
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,F"We are absolutely thrilled by today's
OL,8,Fannouncement because we know this will
OL,9,Fgo a long way towards keeping children
OL,10,Fsafe from harm," it said.
OL,12,F"None of these changes will ever bring
OL,13,Four beautiful Genevieve home. There is
OL,14,Fstill more to do, but today is another
OL,15,Fsignificant milestone.
OL,17,F"Genevieve's legacy continues to grow,
OL,18,Fand we couldn't be prouder of what has
OL,19,Fbeen achieved in her name."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782373690
OL,3,CParents of baby who died at nursery
OL,4,Cwelcome 3,000 extra surprise Ofsted
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FOfsted's announcement is part of a
OL,8,Fgovernment-backed effort to spot
OL,9,Fsafety risks earlier and act faster on
OL,10,Furgent problems.
OL,12,FMore than #8 million a year is being
OL,13,Fallocated to support the work,
OL,14,Fincluding tougher checks before
OL,15,Fnurseries open, and more face-to-face
OL,16,Finterviews with applicants.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782373690
OL,3,CParents of baby who died at nursery
OL,4,Cwelcome 3,000 extra surprise Ofsted
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FThe funding will also strengthen the
OL,8,Fregistration process to assess whether
OL,9,Fapplicants are suitable to run
OL,10,Fchildcare settings, and an upgrade of
OL,11,FOfsted's IT systems will see risk
OL,12,Fassessments accessible to inspectors
OL,13,Fin real time, helping them intervene
OL,14,Fmore quickly.
OL,16,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,17,Fsaid: "Nothing matters more than
OL,18,Fkeeping children safe. Parents should
OL,19,Fbe able to trust that when they leave
OL,20,Ftheir child at a nursery, they are in
OL,21,Fsafe hands.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782373690
OL,3,CParents of baby who died at nursery
OL,4,Cwelcome 3,000 extra surprise Ofsted
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,F"This investment means more surprise
OL,8,FOfsted visits, stronger checks, and
OL,9,Ffaster action where there are concerns
OL,10,F` so risks are spotted early and dealt
OL,11,Fwith quickly.
OL,13,F"Early education gives children the
OL,14,Fbest start in life, and we are making
OL,15,Fsure it is backed by the high
OL,16,Fstandards of care and protection
OL,17,Ffamilies expect."
OL,19,FNursery deputy manager Kate Roughley,
OL,20,Fwas found guilty of killing Genevieve
OL,21,Fand jailed for 14 years in May 2024.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782373690
OL,3,CParents of baby who died at nursery
OL,4,Cwelcome 3,000 extra surprise Ofsted
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FFollowing her death, her parents -
OL,8,FKatie and John - hand delivered a
OL,9,Fletter to Number 10 calling for legal
OL,10,Fchanges to help prevent similar
OL,11,Ftragedies in the future.
OL,13,FEarlier in June, the Minister for
OL,14,FEarly Education Olivia Bailey MP
OL,15,Fconfirmed that updated safer sleep
OL,16,Fwording - developed with experts
OL,17,Fincluding The Lullaby Trust and agreed
OL,18,Fwith Ofsted - will take effect from
OL,19,FSeptember 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782373690
OL,3,CParents of baby who died at nursery
OL,4,Cwelcome 3,000 extra surprise Ofsted
OL,5,Cchecks
OL,7,FOfsted also pledged that safer
OL,8,Fsleeping arrangements will now be
OL,9,Fassessed at every inspection of every
OL,10,Fearly years setting in England.
OL,12,FFurther safeguarding precautions in
OL,13,Fline with the campaign for Gigi could
OL,14,Fbe announced soon with an independent
OL,15,Fpanel currently examining the use of
OL,16,Fdigital devices and CCTV in childcare
OL,17,Fsettings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
